<i>Kids, when your</i>
<i>Uncle Marshall's bus broke down</i>

00:02.880 --> 00:05.160
<i>five miles away</i>
<i>from the Farhampton Inn,</i>

00:05.161 --> 00:06.493
<i>he made a vow.</i>

00:06.495 --> 00:08.512
I can walk that far.

00:08.514 --> 00:12.199
<i>Yes. It was another</i>
<i>exciting installment of...</i>

00:12.201 --> 00:18.455
♪ Marshall versus the machines

00:18.457 --> 00:20.707
♪ Our hero starts his journey

00:20.709 --> 00:23.093
♪ With steely-eyed resolve,
but let's ♪

